<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565400>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 9–13. Parorectis arenaria new species, scanning electron microscopy images. 9) Anterior prothoracic foramen with head removed, ventral view. 10) Anterior prothoracic foramen with head removed, ventrolateral view: AG = antennal groove, CFR = circum-foraminal ridge, LR = lateral ridge, PC = prosternal collar, PL = plectrum. 11) Plectrum. 12) Spicules of cephalic binding patch. 13) Mesotarsal claws, lateral view: PE = pecten." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4565400/files/figure.png" .

